column6: Grape White by Lost Art Liquids is the one of the most popular flavour profile for the smash hit line. Starting off with a sweet and juicy white grape, then blended with a candy apple and topped with a touch of tangy citrus. Perfect for the summer weather right around the corner!
O.G.B is a blue raspberry popsicle with a burst of sweet orange and green apple candy.
Cotton Candy bubble, sweet and sticky this one has the sugary taste of cotton candy with the amazing exhale of american pink bubblegum.
Red Melon bubblegum is a perfect blend of juicy red watermelon paired with sweet sticky american bubblegum.
Tutti Fruity bubblegum is an amazing tutti fruity mixed fruit blend paired with a sweet sticky bubblegum this one is a definite all day.
